snippet: After providing NBC’s Olympic broadcasts with high ratings for his races, Michael Phelps will get help from the Golf Channel, a part of the NBC Sports Group, as the latest celebrity to appear on the swing coach Hank Haney’s “Haney Project.”

headline.main: After Medal Haul, Phelps Plans to Work on His Golf Game
